## High-level description
The `OutboundDocumentRetrievalResp` interface represents the response for an outbound document retrieval request in a healthcare integration system. It extends the `BaseDomainCreate` interface for basic domain object properties and the `OutboundDocumentRetrievalRespTableEntry` interface for specific response data.

## References
- `BaseDomainCreate` (from `@metriport/core/domain/base-domain`)
- `OutboundDocumentRetrievalRespTableEntry` (from `@metriport/core/external/carequality/ihe-gateway/outbound-result`)

## Symbols
### `OutboundDocumentRetrievalResp`
#### Description
This interface defines the structure of the response object for an outbound document retrieval request. It inherits properties for basic domain object management and specific response data related to document retrieval.

#### Inputs
This is an interface, it does not have inputs.

#### Outputs
This is an interface, it does not have outputs.

#### Internal Logic
This is an interface, it does not contain any internal logic. It simply defines the structure of a response object by inheriting properties from other interfaces.
